<br>
As for the spell drop rate,,.. yes Juggs have a large spell drop table, yes they drop some valuable spells, but 95% of their drops are about as common as water and sell for 5pp to a vendor max. There are also other drops in the area you neglect, they drop Undead Dragon Sinew(for the Spirit Wracked Cords, awsome melee item if you're up for the faction work), the nearby Reets drop the Reet Crown for the woodelf illusion quest. If you wish for a well planned event in Seb, I recomend posting in the raid ideas and getting some feedback as to people wanting to go there. We are trying to get more people posting and reading these forums.<br>
<br>
Will there be a seb raid this friday night? Maybe, maybe not. I will be busy friday night and most of saturday, so I probably won't make it.<br>
<br>
I would have loved to help you guys out last Friday night, but I was busy, many people didn't come because they didn't know about it before hand,.. quite sorry for those who waited around a while. Pick-up and unplanned raids take a while to get started and sometimes fall through. Yes the guild needs more planned raids, we're working on it. Getting more people posting here is the first step.<br>
<br>
As for Fayd? I've seen a group of 30 wipe and a group of 9 own him, I would say hes similar in difficulty to King in Chardok, which we raided with 13 and had no deaths. A lot of people were afraid to go, Chardok is a known deathtrap and one bad move can cause a very quick wipe and an expensive or painful CR.<br>
<br>
Our guild priority is what people want and as soon as more people start posting here we will figure out better what people want. Ask the question in the next guild meeting, your priority isn't necessarily the same as the guild's.<br>
<br>
Your spell 'facts'? yes a lot of people don't have all their spells, but our guild spell bank is far from empty. A good solution? I will start a thread in one of these forums for people to post what spells they're missing, so when we pickup a spell we can quickly decide wether it needs to be saved or not, people can also post what spells they have laying around there too. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><br><font color=#A8A8A8>- </font><a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/bdefiantheroesmessageboard>The Defiant Heroes Message Board</a><font color=#A8A8A8> - </font><a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/fdefiantheroesmessageboardfrm18>Planned Raids </a> <font color=#A8A8A8> - </font><a href="http://www.thedefiantheroes.com">Defiant Heroes</a><font color=#A8A8A8> - </font><br><br><table border=0 align=center><tr><td align=center><a href="http://login.ezboard.com/BBSSystem.showUserPaymentScreen" target="_blank">Upgrade your account to ezSupporter...</a></td><td><img src="http://www.ezboard.com/image/spacer.gif" width=15 height=1 border=0></td><td align=center><a href="http://login.ezboard.com/BBSSystem.showUserPaymentScreen" target="_blank">...and never see another ad or pop-up again</a></td></tr></table><CENTER><!-- START BOTTOM AD SCRIPT -->
